This is what homeschooling can look like…. 
I get lots of questions about our home school journey so I’d like to start sharing here and there. Today’s class was at a local beach where we meet once a month with a marine biologist. The small class of other homeschoolers will have a lesson and then will go out and search for the creatures they just learned about. If y’all know me, yall know this class isn’t just for him.😌 Anyway, I love that learning doesn’t have to be confined to the classroom and Mother Nature is my favorite teacher. 😊
Feel free to ask questions…
